{"tid":2022003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派帶頭攬炒 港人無任歡迎！","createTime":"2020-05-18T05:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T16:53:17.000Z","uid":136591,"like":578,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"dd57bff5a3498a5b5145925eb85663926f308326","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"相信內會崩壞令大家都好嬲，無力感好重。<br />\n其實無力感由14年雨革開始，就一直加重。<br />\n直至2019年，香港人發起波瀾壯闊反送中革命，令我地重拾一點同中共制衡既香港民族決心。更令國際社會重新認識香港，重新檢視香港與中共既關係。<br />\n<br />\n去到正題，今日強硬選主席，點算好？<br />\n泛民係議會又阻唔到；制度外抗爭（街頭勇武）又好似去到樽頸位。<br />\n我地做咩好？<br />\n<br />\n太極中有一個重要技巧叫：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>借力打力<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n中共建制急不及待加速管治香港，背後一定做好政治計算，如：美國取消關係法等。我地宜家要做既就係，令中共加速管治香港的政治成本加重，令佢同我地一齊死。簡單黎講係：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">攬炒</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n點做好？<br />\n我地借力打力，順立法會崩壞去攬炒中共！<br />\n對內方面：<br />\n一） 持續抗爭，令國際社會持續關注香港。（呢到特別詳細講下）<br />\n（我地要有新方式：勇武更勇武，和理非更勇武，要有爆炸性新聞，要令全球各大報章頭條都係香港！）<br />\n二） 鋪天蓋地對內宣傳<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建制派帶頭攬炒香港</span></span>，破壞香港法治，令香港經濟一落千丈。從而令更多搵食撚歸邊，令更多港人明白一國兩制已死。<br />\n三） 泛民JR內會主席選舉，令國際重新檢視香港法治制度。<br />\n四）黃圈，35＋繼續做！<br />\n對外方面：<br />\n一） Twitter, Facebook, Instagram 落力傳遞香港淪陷訊息，最好就拉埋武漢肺炎黎講，令外國人深明中共可惡之處。<br />\n二） 加強與外國政治官員交流，加強港人與外國政治聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n其實大家唔洗驚，佢搶得立會主席，最好就立埋23條立埋國歌法。得一個結果，就係港人受害，國際制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際會點制裁？<br />\n取消國際系、信用評級下降、打仗（根據宜家國際政治走向，係真係有機會重現現代八國聯軍。</span><br />\n<br />\n攬炒就係咁既意思。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">我地要中共都付出同樣代價！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抱住攬炒心態，對方一點點既加壓就係我地爭取國際援助既一點點機會！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n天琦係2016年「捍衛民主 香港獨立」集會中講過：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黎明前既黑暗，係至撚黑暗！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">點樣走向光明？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家香港兒女要萬眾一心，再次上路。</strong></span></span><br />\n再重現200萬人集會、全港人\u001d鍊、全港連儂。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3428mJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3428mJ.gif&h=35a71b26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2745e9507ad536337832aa0e22ee80a46fc7412d","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"f52636d387edf16f6845105a7e9435a1edc62348","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"abf4b45c374c7a751ec6a6b4dea8ba2ef4ab4666","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"069f7e6655a3a479205de85a820e9fadd0d0d340","tid":2022003,"uid":34409,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"其實一向要攬炒既係 親中派"},{"pid":"4706156f0e08124fddbb95ef3f48352f9bb8d85d","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"069f7e6655a3a479205de85a820e9fadd0d0d340","tid":2022003,"uid":34409,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"其實一向要攬炒既係 親中派"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:31:36.000Z","msg":"話比全香港人知！<br />\n佢地一直搶輿論話係我地攬炒！<br />\n我地要搶返個輿論"},{"pid":"5cb0bb4685ea44b49a7611f6248c4837f04be7a9","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"6c0f7876d527c21574fe33cafaa4bb4c40cab804","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"2a7845b7cb857747744ea8ae9ea31122c57cc51c","tid":2022003,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c46730c7e4aac4abdb696848f001dbff13c7f7","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"c319253e66dcb7bdd04d5f92122fa6a689173f45","tid":2022003,"uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同少數派一齊鬥紅同攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"49ad38a597ac3cef311c1c860602bb6141eb08d1","tid":2022003,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"去discuss BK開post講啦"},{"pid":"c05ed0ee37a18a791ec418a5d1f5e74d0aad6f00","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYSLBX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYSLBX0.jpg&h=5c7be22b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3331c47fa827e0ba176fefad8a45de21d0a78f58","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49ad38a597ac3cef311c1c860602bb6141eb08d1","tid":2022003,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"去discuss BK開post講啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285b63504c38805b1ac7067e944bda91a18af54a","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"建制派帶頭攬炒香港"},{"pid":"44b1288c7e1779aac78fc56018bc70aaa13e9e3c","tid":2022003,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"攬炒香港 建制挾餸"},{"pid":"96a68ea51795ffebb1b364daa71253264968b76b","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"大家要有遠見<