豪<br />\n其實只要一日美國唔知<br />\n加息先可傷到支那人民幣<br />\n人民幣仍然可透過香港無限印<br />\n然後反映在磚頭通脹上面<br />\n香港樓價負擔指數由2011年11，升到現在20<br />\n香港人咁多年係白做<br />\n<br />\n香港人工資10年間跌左一半 (以樓市購買力計算)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fssOfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fssOfS</a>"},{"pid":"ae0e4a20bf6967922cde4ce46b4c959fc57094cf","tid":2022003,"uid":274870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"都話呢啲奶共派係賣港賊架啦,<br />\n依家仲衰到要帶頭攬炒香港, 賤格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab2ba6f32ffcf9807621fb89ff123421963a7ef","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"125e60482927be87ecbc8549c1cb9113780a634e","tid":2022003,"uid":7936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"帶頭搞亂香港"},{"pid":"1061851474185ad66bcc96cfd1c08666abb774a2","tid":2022003,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"攬炒焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb73a39680f14d75ae3ac836cb6db9f27707ec17","tid":2022003,"uid":86649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d65108b7dbf39278c46b342f928faca9717cbac","tid":2022003,"uid":154892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ad00d6fabc08c7c081b157bb3de2d75c1856a3","tid":2022003,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"930c3f61146e8c02783eab444501eb1bdf623a70","tid":2022003,"uid":268443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"香港沒有建制派, 只有親共派"},{"pid":"3748ba8d12916cd620e01d6f1d69abd6